- Mail Online, 12 Jun 2019: https://www.dailymail.co.uk/wires/ap/article-7131813/Congo-officials-chasing-boy-Ebola-entered-Uganda.html
- STAT News, 11 Jun 2019: https://www.statnews.com/2019/06/11/uganda-confirms-first-ebola-case-outside-outbreak-in-democratic-republic-of-congo/
